snippet.title: Gotham by Gaslight: The Victorian Batman Game That Was Cancelled (1080P)
snippet.description:
Check out my new channel fromsoftserve where I play souls games and say kinda funny things: https://youtu.be/Kr-dCZeCSAw Topaz Labs has some awesome software I personally use: https://topazlabs.com/ref/906/?campaign=may2022 (I do make a small amount if you buy from them) This is an ad-free channel, so if you'd like to support my work, please consider buying merch at SnazzyAI.com, joining my Patreon for $1, or clicking the affiliate links below. Cheers! :) Support the channel by buying SnazzyAI merch: https://snazzyai.com/ (for every product sold, a tree is planted!) Want to try AI upscaling for yourself? You can go here: https://topazlabs.com/video-enhance-ai/ref/906/?campaign=feb2021 (If you decide to purchase anything, I make a small percentage. The free trial is snazzy btw) Please consider supporting the channel! :)
Patreon: https://www.patreon.com/snazzyai
PayPal: https://www.paypal.com/donate?hosted_button_id=4HG2P6RDNYMU8

When you blow your whole budget on the cape physics. Money well spent, I say. Shame this game never came out, but of the test footage we do have, I wanted to present it in the best light possible. 

#gothambygaslight #batman #batmangame
